OL,3,CArrest after Glider bus set on fire
OL,4,Cduring disorder
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a Glider
OL,7,Fbus was set on fire during sporadic
OL,8,Fdisorder in Northern Ireland earlier
OL,9,Fthis month.
OL,11,FViolence flared in several areas three
OL,12,Fweeks ago after a graphic video clip
OL,13,Femerged of a man being stabbed in
OL,14,Fnorth Belfast.
OL,16,FA 29-year-old man was arrested in east
OL,17,FBelfast on Monday on suspicion of a
OL,18,Fnumber of offences including attempted
OL,19,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
