OL,3,CArrest after Glider bus set on fire
OL,4,Cduring disorder
OL,6,FHe was also arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Farson endangering life with intent and
OL,8,Friot.
OL,10,FThe arrest comes after a Glider was
OL,11,Fset on fire, and an arson attack on
OL,12,Fproperties in the McMaster Street area
OL,13,Fof Belfast on June 9.
OL,15,FThe man remained in police custody on
OL,16,FMonday afternoon as police enquiries
OL,17,Fcontinue.
